OL,6,FIt added that Dr Shokouh-Amiri
OL,7,Fcompleted a course on professional
OL,8,Fboundaries, has an "otherwise
OL,9,Funblemished career" and was supported
OL,10,Fby extensive testimonials which
OL,11,F"demonstrated his excellence as a
OL,12,Fclinician".
OL,14,FThe Tribunal concluded there is a "low
OL,15,Frisk of Dr Shokouh-Amiri putting
OL,16,Fpatients at a risk of unwarranted
OL,17,Fharm" and gave him a warning.
