OL,6,FAllegations were made about
OL,7,Finappropriate behaviour involving six
OL,8,Fpatients, relating to when Dr Shokouh-
OL,9,FAmiri worked in Guernsey.
OL,11,FThe proven allegations include that he:
OL,13,FThe Medical Specialist Group
OL,14,Fpreviously confirmed that Dr Shokouh-
OL,15,FAmiri worked for them from 31 October
OL,16,F2016 to 31 August 2019 when he left
OL,17,Fthe partnership and he has not seen
OL,18,Fpatients in Guernsey since January
